## ğŸ” Key Insights

- Top 20% of customers contribute over 60% of total revenue.
- Technology and Office Supplies drive high profit margins.
- Discounts donâ€™t always lead to higher sales.
- Standard Class shipments account for maximum orders, but at lower profitability.

