## ğŸ’» How to Use

1. Download [Tableau Desktop](https://www.tableau.com/products/desktop) (free trial available)
2. Clone this repo or download the `.twb` file
3. Open `PROJECT.twb` in Tableau
4. If dataset is external, you may need to:
   - Relink the data source (`sample_data.csv`)
   - Refresh extracts (if used)

